				<td colspan="2"><span>for all game practical purposes, all you'll ever need is the DE mask.
<br />

<br />
it has better vision, it'll shrink ya (handy if ya a kitty bard in a raid in tunnels) and it will allow ya into evil cities where your would normally be KOS. (trick is have illusion up as ya enter city, and as soon as ya zone, re apply it, and hope no guards right by zone in)
<br />

<br />
the others are for roleplaying, if ya think about it, a bard is a performer, so why not increase your abilities with makeup (illusions) take on different roles.
<br />

<br />
