				<td colspan="2"><span>As previously mentioned in these forums, the Shade Silk Robe is wearable by ALL, and is usually available in the bazaar for only a few plat, or x amount of tradeskill time.  
<br />

<br />
It's convenient when you want to pretend to be a monk or play caster or whatever.  Put it on and refuse to tank!
<br />

<br />
Another fine source for illusions (albeit temporary) are potions from boxes, barrels, other containers in LDoN.  I'll crack open a chest, grab the potion, and bing, I'm a dorf, or troll, or some other absurd race weilding a lute.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
 </span></td>
